  {
    "startTime": 99.4,
    "endTime": 100.4,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.48,
    "endTime": 104.5,
    "text": "So, how are we gonna raise money for these poor, broken, little children?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.58,
    "endTime": 106.08,
    "text": "Let's do a charity calendar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.16,
    "endTime": 107.58,
